WEBVTT

00:00:00.000 --> 00:00:02.600
After they ran off, I rushed back to the hotel

00:00:02.600 --> 00:00:04.200
and called my assistance provider,

00:00:04.200 --> 00:00:06.000
who helped me plan what to do next.

00:00:06.300 --> 00:00:08.600
Their calm professionalism helped me with my shock

00:00:08.600 --> 00:00:10.700
and made me realise how lucky I had been.
